- Ah...

110
00:04:27,049 --> 00:04:29,399
How did I get so lucky?

111
00:04:29,443 --> 00:04:31,401
Is it okay if she stays?

112
00:04:31,445 --> 00:04:32,750
- Uh, sure.
Yeah.

113
