- Thank you.
Come here, sweetheart.

114
00:04:35,405 --> 00:04:37,929
I am fine.
It looks worse than it is.

115
00:04:37,973 --> 00:04:39,757
Your mother's a klutz.

116
00:04:39,801 --> 00:04:41,585
