the surgeries in Mexico?

173
00:06:44,186 --> 00:06:46,449
- No, that--
that was sarcasm.

174
00:06:46,493 --> 00:06:47,885
- That was genius.

175
00:06:47,929 --> 00:06:49,583
Mexico's opening tons
of new clinics

176
00:06:49,626 --> 00:06:51,454
in response to our
skyrocketing medical costs.

177
00:06:51,498 --> 00:06:53,543
