It erodes our hospital.

828
00:37:19,715 --> 00:37:22,588
And American hospitals
are eroded enough.

829
00:37:22,631 --> 00:37:25,112
And, Max, the other thing
I gotta tell you,

830
00:37:25,155 --> 00:37:26,548
